{"page_id": 55583, "slug": "Tsubame_Suzuhara", "title": "Tsubame Suzuhara", "display_title": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Tsubame Suzuhara</span>", "namespace": 0, "content_model": "wikitext", "language": null, "wikitext": "{{expand}}\n[[File:Tsubame.png|thumb|Tsubame in her first contact with Rei Ayanami]]\nTsubame Suzuhara is the daughter of [[Toji Suzuhara]] and [[Hikari Horaki]] featured in [[Evangelion: 3.0 + 1.0]]. She is a small baby and, under the influence of her mother, [[Rei Ayanami| Rei Ayanami]] (Miss Lookalike) builds a relationship of affection and care with her.\n\nApparently, Tsubame is named after the ''Tsubame'' trains at service in the ''Kyushu Shinkansen''.\n\n==Gallery==\n{{MontageBox\n|float   = center\n|columns = 2\n|title   = Tsubame concept arts\n|colour  = beige\n|bgcolor =\n|borderless = \n|image1  = [[File:Tsubame Suzuhara Proposal Moyoco Anno.jpg|thumb|Proposal by Moyoco Anno]]\n|image2  = [[File:Tsubame Suzuhara Settei Nishigori 1.jpg|thumb|Settei Nishigori]]\n|image3  = [[File:Tsubame Suzuhara Settei.jpg|thumb|Settei]]\n|image4  = [[File:Tsubame Suzuhara Front.jpg|thumb|Tsubame final design]]\n|caption =\n}}", "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table align=\"center\" style=\"border:2px solid lightseagreen; width:85%; background:honeydew;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/180px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"101\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/270px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/360px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 2x\" /></a></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<p><big><b>\"<i>Making something... Nurturing something is really great. You can see and learn so many things from the process.</i>\"</b></big><br />\nPlease help improve this article or section by <b>expanding it.</b><br />\n<small>If you have questions on what to improve/expand, please discuss on the talk page.</small>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Tsubame.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/3/3c/Tsubame.png/300px-Tsubame.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"125\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3c/Tsubame.png/450px-Tsubame.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3c/Tsubame.png/600px-Tsubame.png 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Tsubame in her first contact with Rei Ayanami</figcaption></figure>\n<p>Tsubame Suzuhara is the daughter of <a href=\"/Toji_Suzuhara\" title=\"Toji Suzuhara\">Toji Suzuhara</a> and <a href=\"/Hikari_Horaki\" title=\"Hikari Horaki\">Hikari Horaki</a> featured in <a href=\"/Evangelion:_3.0_%2B_1.0\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Evangelion: 3.0 + 1.0\">Evangelion: 3.0 + 1.0</a>. She is a small baby and, under the influence of her mother, <a href=\"/Rei_Ayanami\" title=\"Rei Ayanami\"> Rei Ayanami</a> (Miss Lookalike) builds a relationship of affection and care with her.\n</p><p>Apparently, Tsubame is named after the <i>Tsubame</i> trains at service in the <i>Kyushu Shinkansen</i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\">Gallery</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tsubame_Suzuhara&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Gallery\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table style=\"float: center; clear: center; width: 1px; text-align: center; vertical-align: center; font-size: 90%; background-color: ; border: 1px solid #aaaaaa; margin: 1em;\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"background: beige; font-size: 120%; text-align: center\" colspan=\"2\"><b>Tsubame concept arts</b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Tsubame_Suzuhara_Proposal_Moyoco_Anno.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Tsubame_Suzuhara_Proposal_Moyoco_Anno.jpg/300px-Tsubame_Suzuhara_Proposal_Moyoco_Anno.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"211\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Tsubame_Suzuhara_Proposal_Moyoco_Anno.jpg/450px-Tsubame_Suzuhara_Proposal_Moyoco_Anno.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/48/Tsubame_Suzuhara_Proposal_Moyoco_Anno.jpg/600px-Tsubame_Suzuhara_Proposal_Moyoco_Anno.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Proposal by Moyoco Anno</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei_Nishigori_1.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/83/Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei_Nishigori_1.jpg/300px-Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei_Nishigori_1.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"212\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/83/Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei_Nishigori_1.jpg/450px-Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei_Nishigori_1.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/83/Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei_Nishigori_1.jpg/600px-Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei_Nishigori_1.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Settei Nishigori</figcaption></figure>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei.jpg/300px-Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"336\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei.jpg/450px-Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cd/Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei.jpg/600px-Tsubame_Suzuhara_Settei.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Settei</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Tsubame_Suzuhara_Front.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/84/Tsubame_Suzuhara_Front.jpg/300px-Tsubame_Suzuhara_Front.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" wid